videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. drives down the lane and attacks the rim with an epic one-handed jam in the first half.
videos.headline: Jackson dunks all over Indiana

videos.description: Miles Bridges rises up for back-to-back blocks and doesn't let Indiana score a basket.
videos.headline: Indiana can't get past Bridges

videos.description: Miles Bridges scores a basket over Indiana defenders and draws the foul for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Bridges hits jumper for smart and-1

videos.description: Lourawls Nairn Jr. dishes it to Jaren Jackson Jr. who comes out of nowhere and throws it down at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Nairn, Jackson connect for alley-oop jam

videos.description: Despite being up at halftime, Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo says lack of offensive boards is hurting them.
videos.headline: Spartans need to be better on the boards in second half

videos.description: Zach McRoberts grabs Juwan Morgan's miss and dishes it back to Morgan for a tough layup and a chance for a three-point play.
videos.headline: McRoberts' board leads to Indiana and-1

videos.description: Freddie McSwain deflects Jaren Jackson Jr.'s pass and goes coast-to-coast for a two-handed dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: McSwain steals and slams for Indiana

videos.description: Lourawls Nairn Jr. and Joshua Langford knock in a couple of three-pointers to extend Michigan State's lead to 51-41 against Indiana.
videos.headline: Spartans show off from distance

videos.description: Devonte Green dishes to a wide-open Freddie McSwain who finishes at the rim with an easy dunk to shrink Indiana's deficit.
videos.headline: Indiana's Green feeds McSwain for two-handed jam

videos.description: Cassius Winston finds Matt McQuaid in traffic, who drills a triple to give Michigan State a 4-point lead with less than a minute left in the game.
videos.headline: Winston creates crucial basket for Spartans
